Interface Board

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SudokuBoard

    public interface Board
    Class that allows creation, modification and access to a board. A board's items have a "correct" value, and user's are able to enter both "input" values and "draft" input values.
    Author:
    Hayden Smith, Laura Hodges, Jerome Robins, Steven Falconieri
